{
  "texts": [
    "In 2020, Transformer [30] was introduced to computer vision, ViT [9] and DeiT [29] divide images into sequences to input into Transformer.",
    "Although Transformer has proven its feasibility in CV applications, it is still challenging in the field of object detection, especially multi-vehicle object detection and pedestrian object detection.Pyramid Visual Transformer (PVT [31]) is proposed for extracting features like structures in CNNs.",
    "PVT has shown excellent performance in object detection.",
    "Swin Transformer [20], as one of PVT, introduces non-overlapping window division and restricts self-attention to each local window.",
    "To exchange information between different local areas, its windowing is specially designed to move between two adjacent self-attention layers."
  ]
}